16)Write a program to initialize an integer array with values and check if a given number is present in the array or not. If the number is not found, it will print -1 else it will print the index value of the given  number in the arrayâ€‹

Ex1) Array elements are  {1,4,34,56,7} 

and the search element is 90

O/P: -1

Ex2)Array elements are  {1,4,34,56,7} 

and the search element is 56

O/P: 4 



public class search {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		int[] haystack = {5, 4, 3, 9, 1, 7, 9};
		int needle = 9;
		int index = -1;
		
		for (int i = 0; i < haystack.length; i++) {
			if (haystack[i] == needle) {
				index = i + 1;
				break;
			}
		}

		System.out.println(index);
	}

}
